Homework 1 - Using BeautifulSoup and Pandas

(1) Using the QB stats on fantasy football league page (year 2015 only):

"https://www.fantasypros.com/nfl/reports/leaders/qb.php?year=2015"

(2) The page in (1) contains the table of QB scores (Total, Game played and Average)
in 2015.

(3) Parse the page and generate the matching CSV file.
Store it as a file.

(4) Use the matplotlib to plot the bar-chart that its X-axile represents the average score
and Y-axile represents the counts of number of QBs that has a given average score.
